title: The Great Acorn Robbery feat. Katy Mixon and Diedrich Bader
dc:creator: WBUR
description: Katy Mixon (American Housewife, Minions) and Diedrich Bader (American Housewife, Veep) headline this Seneca tale about an industrious squirrel and the sneaky critters who pilfer her prized acorns.
